name: PS_17_bw16_dln
description: v4W.ENko - "PS_17_bw16_dln". The basic "PseudoRandom" is creating 16 vertices to generate polylines with the "MetaBall Algorithm". The only grayscale gamma is used.  "Pattern Standardization" series of "MetaBall" structure transformed into abstract 3d. The "centroids" of the result polylines are used to generate a crystal structure with "delaunay" system. "Cross connected live patterns" are interactive with each other.
